terestingly, the bug vanishes if &quot;bottom: 0px&quot; is replaced with &quot;top: 0px&quot; (the position, incidentally, does not change) in the code on <a href="http://html5.ouvaton.org/bug2.html" class="postlink">http://html5.ouvaton.org/bug2.html</a>, but replacing the JavaScript with equivalent HTML also fixes the problem, so there is clearly something slightly more complex going on here.<br /><br />-- <br />&amp;<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=52">and</a> — Fri Mar 23, 2007 9:07 pm</p><hr />
